# Demo Images for Lens Feature

Place 2-3 known-good test images here for the hackathon demo:

1. A clear dashboard warning light photo (e.g., check engine light, oil pressure warning)
2. A readable service book or receipt photo
3. (Optional) Another warning light or maintenance document

Recommended naming:
- `warning-light-engine-check.jpg`
- `service-book-sample.jpg`
- `warning-light-oil-pressure.jpg`

These images will be used to demonstrate the Lens feature reliably during the demo.
